requirement: "C-0-11] MUST support the shell command cmd testharness. Upgrading device implementations from an earlier Android version without a persistent data block MAY be exempted from C-0-11. "
"C-3-1] MUST implement adb via local-area network (such as Ethernet or Wi-Fi). "

"C-3-2] MUST provide drivers for Windows 7, 8 and 10, allowing developers to connect to the device using the adb protocol. If device implementations support adb connections to a host machine via Wi-Fi, they: "
"C-4-1] MUST have the AdbManager#isAdbWifiSupported() method return true. If device implementations support adb connections to a host machine via Wi-Fi and includes at least one camera, they: "
"C-5-1] MUST have the AdbManager#isAdbWifiQrSupported() method return true. Dalvik Debug Monitor Service (ddms) "
